&lt;p&gt;Simply’s mission is to make the pursuit of creative hobbies simple and fun. Our top-grossing apps Simply Piano, Simply Guitar, Simply Sing, and Simply Draw put us on the fast track to building the world’s largest global consumer subscription service that’s revolutionizing how we spend our time at home. With over a million monthly downloads and hundreds of thousands of daily learners around the world, we’re redefining creative learning at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;What Senior AI Research Engineers do at Simply&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Senior AI Research Engineers at Simply develop algorithmic solutions that power new innovative features and continuously improve existing ones, with a strong emphasis on training AI / ML models as a core part of the role. The work spans a wide range of domains - from training generative AI and LLM-based models to create musical content at scale for Simply Piano, through building deep learning computer vision models that enhance user drawings in Simply Draw, to developing real-time audio ML models for music transcription that elevate feedback in Simply Guitar.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will take full end-to-end ownership of cutting-edge algorithms and AI models - leading the process from ideation and research, through development, to production-grade implementation and engineering within Simply’s products. This includes not only designing and building AI models, but also ensuring robust, efficient, and scalable integration into the app - directly shaping the experience of millions of users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;Who you are and what you’ve done&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Master&#39;s degree in Electrical Engineering, Computer Science, Physics, or a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in designing and implementing AI/ML algorithms, with a strong focus on signal processing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience working across the full ML lifecycle - from data acquisition and model training to production implementation and ongoing product iteration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Moves fast, with strong engineering instincts, able to choose the right level of complexity to drive real-world impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A get things done attitude with a strong sense of ownership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A team player with excellent communication and collaboration skills; able to convey complex ideas clearly to technical and non-technical partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional analytical and problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A fast learner, willing to try things out of your comfort zone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in speech, audio, or music-related domains - Advantage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simply&#39;s mission is to make the pursuit of creative hobbies simple and fun for all.&lt;/strong&gt; Our top-grossing apps Simply Piano, Simply Guitar, Simply Sing, and Simply Draw put us on the fast track to building the world&#39;s largest consumer subscription service for creative learning. With over a million monthly downloads and hundreds of thousands of daily learners, we&#39;re building the AI creative companion for every home.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Senior Business Strategy Analyst&amp;nbsp; to own end-to-end business and strategic analysis across the company. In this role, you will partner closely with the Head of Strategy, and company leadership to identify growth opportunities, evaluate strategic initiatives, and generate actionable insights that influence the Simply&#39;s direction and performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who you are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You have strong business acumen and strategic thinking capabilities. You thrive in ambiguity&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are excited by identifying opportunities, uncovering insights, and influencing decision-making&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are excited when learning something new and applying itAn amazing people-person and team playerYou do not shy away from accountability&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ve done&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4+ years of experience as a Consultant, Business Analyst, Strategy Analyst, or in a similar analytical role – A MUST&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience analyzing&amp;nbsp; KPIs, measuring business impact, and supporting strategic decision making through data&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;University graduate in a quantitative field&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Worked with data visualization software (Tableau, Redash, Power BI, etc.)&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simply&#39;s mission is to make the pursuit of creative hobbies simple and fun for all.&lt;/strong&gt; Our top-grossing apps Simply Piano, Simply Guitar, Simply Sing, and Simply Draw put us on the fast track to building the world&#39;s largest consumer subscription service for creative learning. With over a million monthly downloads and hundreds of thousands of daily learners, we&#39;re building the AI creative companion for every home.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Senior Product Designer do at Simply:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re expanding our world-class team and looking for a passionate, highly experienced Product Designer to join one of our multidisciplinary product teams. In this role, you&#39;ll collaborate with engineers, product managers, marketers, and musicians to have a direct impact on our product and business, shaping the experience of millions of users worldwide.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You live and breathe design. You&#39;re passionate about crafting smart, effective, and beautiful experiences. You care deeply about understanding users and translating insights into meaningful product solutions. You&#39;re excited to play a key role in designing new products and initiatives in a fast-paced, creative environment.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ve done:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;+5 years of experience designing from a consumer product-focused tech company, having full ownership of the entire product life cycle&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Vast experience designing for mobile and web&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Innovative problem solver - your passion is transforming complex problems into simple and intuitive user experiences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Deep understanding of product, as well as branding, with the ability to take forward the brand vision, marketing needs and make creative ideas come to life&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Understanding of both qualitative and quantitative user data (i.e. A/B testing, surveys, analytics tools, usability testing)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re a highly independent team player. Yes, exactly that. You’re an amazing team player, but don’t need anyone to hold your hand&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You know your craft and tools - up to speed with design trends. Superb knowledge of Figma, Sketch, Photoshop and illustrator and fearless of learning new ones as needed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Visual communication degree - big plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simply&#39;s mission is to make the pursuit of creative hobbies simple and fun for all.&lt;/strong&gt; Our top-grossing apps Simply Piano, Simply Guitar, Simply Sing, and Simply Draw put us on the fast track to building the world&#39;s largest consumer subscription service for creative learning. With over a million monthly downloads and hundreds of thousands of daily learners, we&#39;re building the AI creative companion for every home.&lt;/p&gt;
