&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;In this key engineering role in one of our multidisciplinary product teams, you will take end-to-end ownership of the engineering discipline and tasks that will bring the most impact and joy to millions of learners. All this while quickly learning and adapting to do whatever it takes to solve the unsolvable.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
