&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At least 5 years of extensive software engineering experience, preferably across a variety of technologies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;BSc in Computer Science or equivalent practical experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A team player with amazing verbal and written communication skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Passionate about product and impacting people&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
